leadingComments.value: Set the src to a short bit of url encoded as a silent mp3
NOTE The silence MP3 must be high quality, when web audio sounds are played
in parallel the web audio sound is mixed to match the bitrate of the html sound
0.01 seconds of silence VBR220-260 Joint Stereo 859B

trailingComments.value: disable iOS Airplay (setting the attribute in js doesn't work)

leadingComments.value: disable iOS Airplay (setting the attribute in js doesn't work)

*
 * Ignores device silence mode when using the `WebAudio` backend.
 *
 * Many mobile devices contain a hardware button to mute the ringtone for incoming
 * calls and messages. Unfortunately, on some platforms like iOS, this also mutes
 * wavesurfer's audio when using the `WebAudio` backend. This function creates a
 * temporary `<audio>` element that makes sure the WebAudio backend keeps playing
 * when muting the device ringer.
 *
 * @since 5.2.0
